To all those who've had trouble where it "skips page 30 day trial etc ". I've copied some instructions from Ching_Liu who has uploaded the same torrent. 

What you need to do:
1. Open keygen.exe
2. Choose the correct program to generate serial number. So on the drop down arrow, choose "VideoStudio Pro X5 v15.0". It will then give you a serial number(keep this program running and dont click on the button on the buttom that says "serial" cos then you'v changed your serial number and it wont match the installation code later)
3. Run "VSX5_Ultimate_PF" which is the actual program. It will then take you to a page that says enter Username and Serial number. MANUALLY enter the serial number
4. Then the next page it'll ask you to enter more information. Click "Other Activation Options", select "Phone Corel" option. This will give you and INSTALLATION code
5. Copy this code into the still open keygen program as XXXX-XXXX-XXXX-XXXX-XXXX and generate your ACTIVIATION code. Copy this code in to related area in Corel(you can cut paste this one).
6. Use firewall to stop internet connection of application. Uncheck automatic updates and do not update application.
7.Some security softwares may give warning for Keygen-CORE, it is false positive and don't worry about it.

Theres another file called "VSX5_Ultimate_Bonus" which has those bonus features eg graffiti, blue FX. I didnt need this so didnt install them. 


If you open the folder and dont find the Keygen program, its becos you antivirus has automatically delete it. Then you need to open your antivirus program and restore it. 

Hope that helps.

I forgot to mention a step.
